title: Kid Made Modern My First Arts and Crafts Library
description:
My First Arts & Crafts Supply Library was designed especially for budding crafters. Keeping in mind their small hands and developing fine motor skills, the components are large and easy to grasp, yet artist quality. Includes:

  • 12 round wooden beads
  • 49 fuzzy sticks
  • 14 jumbo fuzzy sticks
  • 20 paper straws
  • 16 jumbo craft sticks
  • 12 colored clothes pins
  • 8 sticker sheets
  • 216 gold foam stickers
  • 15 sticky-backed jewels
  • 16 sticky-backed googly eyes
  • 12 sticky-backed felt circles
  • 2 skeins of yarn (3 yards)
  • 1 skein of twine (3 yards)
  • 13 glitter paper shapes
  • 3 rolls paper tape
  • 12 plastic canvas square 3.15" (square Screen reader support enabled)

Recommended for ages 3 and up.  Made in the USA.
